{
  "text": "14 The visionrelated QoL was assessed with the National Eye Institute Visual Function Questionnaire-25. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] In addition, an inhouse questionnaire for complaints specific to problems with eye movement was included (available from Protocols.io [Questionnaire Eye Movement Complaints] protocols.io/ view/questionnaire-eye-movements-complaints-vrxe57n).",
